# HKWorkoutActivityType.other

**Case**

The constant for a workout that does not match any of the other workout activity types.

## Declaration

```swift
case other
```

## Discussion

If your app uses the [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKWorkoutActivityType/swimming] or [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKWorkoutActivityType/other] activity type, you must explain how your app calculates workout data when sensor information is not available. For more information, see the [https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/watchos/interaction/workout/].
